# Local SQLite database and its transient write-ahead-log files. The schema is
# created on boot and the data is regenerable with `npm run seed` in /server,
# so the .db is a local artifact rather than source -- and keeping it out of the
# repo avoids publishing resident records and password hashes.
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
